summary: An Ordinance authorizing and directing the City Comptroller to draw, and the City Treasurer to pay a warrant in favor of the Clerk of the Superior Court of King County, Washington, on the Cedar River Watershed Condemnation Fund, for the purpose of satisfying the judgment in the Cedar Falls Condemnation case, as provided in Ordinance No. 35647, Cause No. 115338, and declaring an emergency.
